Full Spellbook

Description:
Lists all of the cantrips then all of the leveled spells and in parenthesees, it lists now many uses you have of the spell. See the wiki link up top to learn how to add focus spells and innate spell sections

Spells(Innate): %{selected|repeating_spellinnate_$id_spellroll}
Spells(Focus): %{selected|repeating_spellfocus_$id_spellroll}
Spells(Cantrip): %{selected|repeating_cantrip_$id_spellroll}
Spells(lvl.1-10): %{selected|repeating_normalspells_$id_spellroll}

